  <Method>
    <Step image="">Sear roast. </Step>
    <Step image="">Transfer the pan to the oven and roast until an instant-read thermometer inserted into the thickest part of the tri-tip registers about 125ºF for medium, 20 to 30 minutes. </Step>
    <Step image="">Rest roast. Meanwhile... </Step>
    <Step image="">Combine relish ingredients. </Step>
    <Step image="">Halve roast, slice on bias, serve with relish. </Step>
  </Method>
